Package com.nhn.android.maps

Interface Summary
NMapActivity.OnDataProviderListener Interface for data provider listeners.
NMapCompassManager.OnCompassChangeListener Interface for listeners interested in the state change of compass.
NMapItemizedOverlay.OnFocusChangeListener Interface for listeners interested in when the focused Item changes.
NMapLocationManager.OnLocationChangeListener Interface for listeners interested in the state change of location.
NMapView.OnMapStateChangeListener Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when the state of a map view changed.
NMapView.OnMapViewDelegate Interface definition for a callback to be invoked for the map view delegate.
NMapView.OnMapViewTouchEventListener Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when an event of the map view handled.
 

Class Summary
NMapActivity Base class with code to manage the boring necessities of any activity that displays a NMapView.
NMapCompassManager Compass manager which implements SensorEventListener.
NMapCompassManager.SensorFilter 센서 값의 noise를 제거하기 위한 filtering 클래스.
NMapController A utility class to manage panning and zooming of NMapView.
NMapItemizedOverlay A base class for an NMapOverlay which consists of a list of NMapOverlayItems.
NMapLocationManager Location manager which implements LocationListener.
NMapOverlay Base class representing an overlay which may be displayed on top of a map.
NMapOverlayItem The basic component of any NMapItemizedOverlay.
NMapProjection A Projection serves to translate between the coordinate system of x/y on-screen pixel coordinates and that of latitude/longitude points on the surface of the earth.
NMapView A View which displays a map (with data obtained from the Naver Maps service).
NMapView.LayoutParams LayoutParams for NMapView.
